# Spam Jam Desktop Launcher
#
# Launches the Spam Jam BLE/Bluetooth attack toolkit in a terminal.
# Root privileges are required for Bluetooth hardware access (raw sockets, etc.).
#
# Features:
#   - BLE Advertise All (device name spam)
#   - Interactive BLE scanning + targeted spam/jam
#   - L2Ping flood attacks
#   - RFCOMM connection flooding
#   - BLE Mesh Botnet (multi-device command & control)
#
# For authorized testing / research use only.
